node.text: Love it, this message is important! 😊💜

You are not the problem. It’s the stories we’ve inherited that we don’t like that keeps us from loving the way we want to.

Get on my calendar to feel more at home in your transition into non-monogamy because loving freely should not be this hard.

Link in bio or here: angela-han.com/call

#nonmonogamy #openmarriage #polyamory

goddamn you keep speaking words I need to hear -- thank you so much
